A  VERY  MAGICAL  JOURNEY

CHAPTER ONE

The Magical Dream

Once  upon a time there was a boy named Bob he always dreamed and thought of magic .One day he went to a birthday party,he stayed there for 3 hours straight. He came back to his house and slept.The boy slept very fast beacause he was so tired staying 
in the birthday party,as soon as Bob slept he had a dream in the dream everyone where dissapering and appearing,he ignored everyone and started walking suddenly a very big castle was just infront of him.Bob started walking towards the castle and saw 
many children learning magic there were children learning how to fly on a broom stick,how to make a invisibility potion,how to cast spells and many more Bob ran towards the children who were casting spells but as soon as he started walking all the
children dissapered again. Then some light was coming from the sky it was usually blue after that there was a very loud sound coming from all four directions.Bob was closing his ears then he woke up from bed the alarm clock was making the loud sound.
It was all a dream? 'said Bob'. he woke up from bed got ready for school and he was thinking about the dream all day.


CHAPTER TWO

A WEIRD PERSON


After Bob finished school he was still thinking about the magical dream.He went back home and there was a letter saying 'im going to work now in a school. Teaching children about scienc, you can have lunch on the table there are a few fruits i'll be back
in evening'.Bob went to the table and ate an apple and a orange. As soon as he finished eating the orange a knock came in the door, there was a very weird looking man who was wearing a black robe and a book in his head he was yawning, Bob opened the
door the weird man told 'uh is there any Bob here '. 'Yes im here' said Bob . The weird looking man looked at Bob and came into his house and sat on the couch .The weird looking man said 'come here dont be shy'. Bob came to the weird man and sat on the 
couch . The weird man said 'do you know why im here'.'No' said Bob 'im here to tell you that youll be learning in a magic school, don't think that this is a joke very magic  people can only be here in this school.'But im not magic said Bob 'what your non-
magic' said the weird man. 'No im not im just a simple boy ' said Bob . 'You are not an ordinary boy the king has send me here to let you come to the magic world.
